# Firebase credentials.
# - google-services.json holds Android FCM sender id + API key (public-facing
#   identifiers, but kept out of the public repo by convention).
# - GoogleService-Info.plist is the iOS equivalent.
# - service-account*.json is Firebase Admin SDK / FCM V1 server creds (TRULY
#   secret — uploaded to EAS via `eas credentials` and not used at runtime
#   on disk, but we ignore the pattern in case it lands in the repo).
mobile/google-services.json
mobile/GoogleService-Info.plist
mobile/service-account*.json
mobile/*-firebase-adminsdk-*.json

# TS build info
*.tsbuildinfo
